Title: Roland
Plot: Mulder and Scully investigate the death of a scientist working on advanced propulsion technology. The mentally challenged janitor Roland, who has secretly been completely the scientist's work, is the prime suspect.
GuestStars: Zeljko Ivanek, Garry Davey, James Sloyan, Micole Mercurio, Kerry Sandomirsky, Matthew Walker, David Hurtubise, Sue Mathew
